[SN]TITLE[SN]
Mitsubishi shares jump 16% on news of Nissan stake

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
Shares in Mitsubishi Motors jumped 16.6% following suspension on news Nissan is planning to take a major stake in the embattled carmaker. Nissan itself fell 1.4%.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
